OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely cloudy but with the
OL,6,Fchance of some bright spells,
OL,7,Fespecially for a time this afternoon
OL,8,Fto the east of the Pennines. Later
OL,9,Fcloud will thicken, bringing a chance
OL,10,Fof patchy light rain, especially
OL,11,Facross western hills.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FHill fog will develop over
OL,14,Fthe Pennines, with patchy light rain
OL,15,Flikely at times. Elsewhere generally
OL,16,Fcloudy and dry, although occasional
OL,17,Flight rain may reach North Yorkshire.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
