OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FCloudy with hill fog across
OL,6,Fthe Pennines, and patchy light rain
OL,7,Fgradually easing. Elsewhere mainly dry
OL,8,Fand cloudy, but with bright spells
OL,9,Fgradually developing. Feeling warm and
OL,10,Fhumid. Breezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloudy
OL,13,Fand breezy for much of the period with
OL,14,Fspells of rain at times, mostly
OL,15,Faffecting western hills with drier
OL,16,Fconditions further east. Temperatures
OL,17,Fgradually creeping up, becoming warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
